txt.en: 'Bah. All those spirits banished back to shadow!'
'Fools! You have no conception of my power! I will destroy you all!'
'I suppose I shall just have to summon more.'
'A true shame to lose so many good spirits in such a short time.'
'Well, it seems the area is secure enough for the moment. I shall certainly complain to Mordirith about this intrusion!'
'Who has dismissed my spirits? What fool dares to interfere with my work?'
